                </p>

            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
            <div class="overlay">
                <h3>Melek Nehir DEMIR</h3>
            </div>

            <img src="~/pictures/software engineer.jpg" alt="" />
            <div class="bio">
                <h5>
                    Software Engineer
                </h5>
                <p>
                    It was so strange,that when i was working as a simple software engineer, my friend came up to me with some idea. He said that i was a successful software engineer, and wanted me to work in AcarSoft(when it was not yet founded)! Now all together, we are producing the best & qualified & reliable software!
