                <p>
                    I was born in Ankara, in 1996. I have been in Ankara until i graduated from high school. Then, i earned to privilage to educate in ITU, Istanbul. After I graduated from ITU, Software Engineering. I was mostly thinking about making experience, but what experience is there to work in our own corporation?
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
            <div class="overlay">
                <h3>Ali Rıza OZARSLAN</h3>
            </div>

            <img src="~/pictures/design engineer.jpg" alt="" />
            <div class="bio">
                <h5>
                    Chief Designer
                </h5>

                <p>
                    Your regular old guy; at least this is what my collegues call me :) i love my team, these little guys inspire me, and give me hope greatly! You know i am an old guy and, that i worked in many companies. But trust me, these guys are a whole different level! Love my corporation, inspire from my corporation. And finally, i produce the greatest software designs.
